PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of DONALD JOHN LANGLOIS, of St. Catharines, Ontario, as a member of the Great Lakes Pilotage Authority, Ltd., to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective June 21, 1996, in the place of Gordon Charles Canough, whose term will expire.
